## Fix "Invalid ISO datetime" on PUT updated_at

1. [app/apps/web/app/services/todo.server.ts](app/apps/web/app/services/todo.server.ts): Added `timestampToIso()` helper; `toTodoRow` now sets `due_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, and `deleted_at` (when present) via `new Date(...).toISOString()` so API JSON matches Zod `z.string().datetime()` and PUT optimistic-lock `updated_at` round-trips.

